messages.text: Travis is here with a girl
No. Find out who she is.
I need proof they’re having sex
That’s what I’m paying you for
She just got up and went to the restroom
And he just smiled at me
Could he know you’re a private investigator?
I suspect he smiles at all girls sitting alone in bars
I see you’re cute from the photo on your website. It doesn’t surprise me
I hate that word cute. It’s for dogs
Consider it a compliment. Feel free to expense your drinks
I trust you. What’s he doing now?
She’s back. Looks like she just brushed her hair
I need to know who she is
Looks like they’re heading out. He’s not going to finish his drink
My family has too much invested in this wedding!
Doesn’t appear so. They’ve stopped. One sec
They stopped at a doorway. She pulled out her keys
I just walked past and overheard Travis whisper to her that he thinks I may be following him
Probably because he smiled at me at the bar. I got the feeling he was joking
But now your cover is blown
I can still get you the information you need
They’ve gone in. Hold on a second.
Christa Long on the mailbox. Know her?
I need proof their having sex
I don’t care if it cost more. I need results.
I didn’t see a partner on your website
Former partner. We still work together. Let me get back to you.
I need your help, strictly business
I’m working a case. I need you to follow a guy
A graduate student. The client is his fiancée.
Only if you’ll have dinner with me
We talked about this. It’s over between us
Still don’t know what I did wrong :(
You did nothing wrong. It’s all on me. I’m sorry but i can’t be in a relationship right now
I got made by the subject
You’re the only one I know that knows how to do this kind of work
Only if you tell me what you’re wearing
That’s the deal. Take it or leave it
I don’t believe you. Send a selfie :)
Will you help me or not? I can pay you
Then I won’t cash the check
Remember that ski weekend? We never skied
I’ll do it. Email me the details.
Click below to see what happens next…
